This is a half comical/half video modeling movie. Part of the movie shows a kind of story that a girl is narrating. They tried to create a comical story that ties in with the other models in the movie. The video quality is not bad, the music used during the posing and modeling is pretty good, but they obviously didn't put too much effort with the voice/sound recording. They obviously used the mic on the camcorder versus a production mic. The story is cute to watch, as it's just a very bad "B" movie style, but the posing and modeling part is nice to watch.

Overall, it's not a bad video. The story is a bit entertaining and the girls on the video are very nice. I rather not tell you the plot, as that would be pointless, especially since this is an adult video, so what's the point to telling a plot when it's obvious you want the see the girls. FOR ADULTS ONLY!!!

This one is shot like a mini-movie, with a stupid little plot thread about supernatural harlots who like to strip naked in front of protagonist Karlie Montana. I'm not a fan of hers,  but she looks really cute here. Of the five models depicted, though, the slam dunk is the blisteringly-hot Anita Dark. We need to see more out of her from Peach! Although considering that this production already is several years old, I doubt  that that happens.

Abundant graphic nudity (yes!), abundant footage shot of the ladies from their posterior (double yes!). Overall a very good production and a solid four stars. I just wish that we'd had another naturally-busty model or two in the mix; that would have made it five stars.

Also, and this is something that rarely gets mentioned, I love Peach's soundtracks.  Better than most every other company's in this genre. Sort of am ambient/smooth jazz kind of thing, very mellow. Almost too mellow at times because I've fallen asleep watching a few different Peach productions.
